{
  "stem": "11611.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was a cashier at the PX, she also had control of the cigarette counter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- she offered me-- this was before I really knew her very well, but she offered me un-rationed cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were rationed to a carton a week, that controlled the black market to a fair degree, but she had control of this and she could offer me extra cigarettes if I wanted them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was so dumb and straight laced that I never took any.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She regards that as very peculiar my part.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Says she didn't make that offer to anybody except me, and she can't imagine anybody who would have turned it down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't think in terms of goods or money in those days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was totally unrealistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, Nazi party hierarchy, that's different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were very few Nazi party officials who were German nobility.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a two-- yeah, they were all-- all of them were colleagues from the Nuremberg proceedings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were translators and interpreters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were also a couple, now that I start thinking back on it, a couple of Swiss who were there as interpreters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't let me forget to mention my episodes with the great German airplane designer Willy Messerschmitt, because that was an interesting episode.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Swiss were courting him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Willy Messerschmitt was held in Nuremberg as a material witness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was not a defendant, but had been held for a considerable period of time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he had freedom to wander in the city but everybody was courting Willy Messerschmitt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Messerschmitt airplanes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was a designer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was a famous airplane designer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Messerschmitts were pretty good planes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
